---
---
<section
  class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 overflow-hidden scanline-overlay scanline-bar"
  aria-label="메인 히어로"
>
  <!-- Layered background: gradient + floating particles -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <!-- Radial depth gradient -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-pk-bg via-pk-bg-alt to-pk-bg"></div>
    <!-- Floating pixel particles -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 25%, #FF4422 1.5px, transparent 1.5px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 65%, #3399FF 1.5px, transparent 1.5px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #44BB44 1px, transparent 1px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 25% 75%, #FFCC00 1px, transparent 1px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 75% 15%, #AA44CC 1px, transparent 1px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 60% 85%, #66CCEE 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 200px 200px, 180px 180px, 150px 150px, 170px 170px, 160px 160px, 190px 190px;
      animation: drift 25s linear infinite;
    "></div>
    <!-- Vignette -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,transparent_40%,#0f0f1a_100%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="text-pk-text-secondary text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up">
      POCKET KINGDOM
    </p>

    <!-- Title with glow pulse -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl text-pk-accent animate-fade-up-delay-1 mb-6" style="
      text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,204,0,0.4), 0 0 60px rgba(255,204,0,0.15), 4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    ">
      포켓 왕국
    </h1>

    <!-- Prophecy quote -->
    <blockquote class="pixel-card-glow max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 animate-fade-up-delay-2 text-left">
      <p class="text-pk-accent text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed italic">
        "어둠이 세상을 삼킨 뒤,<br/>
        잊혀진 마석의 빛이 다시 깨어나리라.<br/>
        그 빛을 이끄는 자가 세계를 되찾으리."
      </p>
      <footer class="text-pk-muted text-xs mt-3 not-italic">— 고대의 예언서</footer>
    </blockquote>

    <!-- Tagline -->
    <p class="text-pk-text text-sm md:text-base mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-up-delay-3 text-balance">
      102종의 몬스터와 계약하고, 18가지 타입의 상성을 읽어
      마왕에게 빼앗긴 세계를 되찾아라.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-up-delay-4">
      <a href="/monsters" class="pixel-btn">
        몬스터 도감 보기
      </a>
      <a href="/story" class="pixel-btn-ghost">
        스토리 읽기
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll hint -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-pk-muted text-xs animate-float" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="block mb-1 text-center text-[10px] tracking-widest">SCROLL</span>
    ▼
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes drift {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-80px) translateX(20px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(-160px) translateX(0); }
  }
</style>
